{"id": 2459, "genre": 1001, "title": "互联网上，你都有过哪些不经意暴露“真实自我”的时刻？", "description": "防不胜防啊。（题图来自：iStock © uzenzen）", "record_count": 2021, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180709164103mFaGCkHL4ri5OTbN.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-07-11T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 292096, "content": "搜索记录", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377387}, {"id": 292098, "content": "网络重构了我", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392735}, {"id": 292099, "content": "pyq吐槽各种东西的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1386282}, {"id": 292102, "content": "用各种小号默默吐槽的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1281633}, {"id": 292104, "content": "当别人说出了自己心声 大方点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 602753}, {"id": 292616, "content": "热搜。关注。推荐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388681}, {"id": 292106, "content": "去看别人的空间 但是因为不是黄钻 不能删除记录 而正好不想让那个人知道我来过他空间的时候 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1314591}, {"id": 292875, "content": "发朋友圈忘记选分组可见。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403601}, {"id": 292108, "content": "“猜您喜欢”……", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1361713}, {"id": 292109, "content": "不小心发了丑照，忘记屏蔽陌生人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1259287}, {"id": 292111, "content": "qq空间的留言板", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381523}, {"id": 292114, "content": "匿名的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396700}, {"id": 292115, "content": "无聊，不断刷文章时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396704}, {"id": 292116, "content": "发贴吧截图给网友，被看到百度账号是什么，一搜索就能看见我当年关注的各种贴吧…高中吧大学吧兴趣吧都在里面?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1216775}, {"id": 292117, "content": "发东西带有个人喜好以及日常相关信息的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377975}, {"id": 292118, "content": "好奇心太重了\n好奇心害死人\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395680}, {"id": 292888, "content": "在别人说的很对的时候，忍不住点个赞，就这时。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1403972}, {"id": 292121, "content": "问题直击真实的自己，躲不掉的坑", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396757}, {"id": 292123, "content": "不受理智在空间疯狂骂人的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395670}, {"id": 292124, "content": "百度Q号能搜到贴吧带有Q号的发言记录，从而暴露了贴吧ID", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 799183}, {"id": 292125, "content": "我不是针对任何人，我就是专门来diss起点评论的", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379987}, {"id": 292126, "content": "网友聊天谈心的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396793}, {"id": 292127, "content": "在漂流瓶的世界里", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1388689}, {"id": 292129, "content": "...玩游戏胜利/通关的时候\n开心的像个小孩子", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1392964}, {"id": 292130, "content": "你浏览过后，淘宝推送的各类奇奇怪怪的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1213780}, {"id": 292131, "content": "\n关注这些有啥用，像我把钱放在余额宝每天有利息，还可以每天在首页输入7030426领取余额宝消费红包，一般都是几块钱运气爆棚的时候有28.8元可充话费，水电费，超市购物的时候用余额宝（注意，余额宝支付）消费就可以抵扣红包，每天可领一次，别赞要脸", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396834}, {"id": 292643, "content": "生气的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1399537}, {"id": 292391, "content": "和不认识的人，基本上每天都在暴露的！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1112170}, {"id": 292140, "content": "百度推广。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266221}, {"id": 292141, "content": "为小编点赞", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273908}, {"id": 292143, "content": "打游戏时，喷队友菜鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 605615}, {"id": 292144, "content": "说qq悄悄话的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1396426}, {"id": 292146, "content": "翻墙打开tumblr时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1008226}, {"id": 292152, "content": "浏览器，历史", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 292153, "content": "说是不告诉人家，我tumblr，或者twitter帐号啥的，结果截图没注意就发过去了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416657}, {"id": 296249, "content": "猜我喜欢", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853127}, {"id": 298838, "content": "某天一女老师投屏讲课，用搜狗想打经验，第一个跳出来的是精液..", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 950448}, {"id": 293978, "content": "深夜微博，每次灵魂拷问自己以后，忍不住发的，第二天醒来总是想要挖个洞自己钻进去", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1369151}, {"id": 292191, "content": "表达自己态度时候会很严肃，无意中也就被暴露了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1312559}, {"id": 293218, "content": "输入法", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1321131}, {"id": 292199, "content": "被各种广告营销电话骚扰时，有一种想捶死自己的冲动....只怪自己那颗真诚相待的心?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395800}, {"id": 292462, "content": "用朋友手机看电影没有清除记录的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1398483}, {"id": 292719, "content": "别人分享悲伤经理时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1398449}, {"id": 292212, "content": "忘了在朋友圈屏蔽当事人都时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1395388}, {"id": 292727, "content": "微博上我的点赞内容会推给好友，是不是有病？", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1379935}, {"id": 292224, "content": "当别人和我开始用一样的小众软件", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367702}, {"id": 292737, "content": "自己给自己点赞的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1401945}, {"id": 296577, "content": "被别人看出是小号的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1422264}, {"id": 293764, "content": "来到这的一刻起 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1408229}, {"id": 300168, "content": "发语音没用变音器", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 795920}]}